    Come see this LOVELY NEWLY REMODELED home located in a quiet neighborhood of FLORIDA! This home is in turn-key condition with the upgrades it offers. Open floor layout from Living room, dining room and kitchen. Oversized windows allow plenty of natural daylight. Vinyl floors throughout. Modern eat in kitchen with white self closing cabinets, granite countertop and island, trendy backsplash & gorgeous fresh out the box stainless steel appliances! Ground level bedroom, half bath, laundry area & enclosed den complete the ground level! Upper level offers 3 additional bedrooms & a brand new Full bath with tiled walls & floors. Ample yard space to garden or to enjoy your morning coffee or Summer entertaining. Shed available for storage with newly blacktopped driveway. This home offers a new roof, new siding, & new windows aside from many interior upgrades. Minutes to local wineries, shopping, Garnett Health & a convenient commuter location to & from NYC. A must see. Book your tour today!
